v}}.spec.template.spec.containers.name={{ubuntu}}.image should specify the image with a digest","tags":["security","checkmarx","kics"]}},{"id":"Privacy Violation in Error Messages - 7311612736703362877 (sast)","name":"Privacy Violation in Error Messages","helpUri":"https://checkmarx.com/resource/documents/en/34965-67042-checkmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"Method Cx58065ed3 at line 178 of /frontend/__tests__/routes/manage-organization-members.test.tsx includes PII in Error in the error message. This may result in a Privacy Violation.\n\n","markdown":"Method Cx58065ed3 at line 178 of /frontend/__tests__/routes/manage-organization-members.test.tsx includes PII in Error in the error message. This may result in a Privacy Violation.\n\n"},"fullDescription":{"text":"Method Cx58065ed3 at line 178 of /frontend/__tests__/routes/manage-organization-members.test.tsx includes PII in Error in the error message. This may result in a Privacy Violation.\n\n"},"properties":{"security-severity":"2.0","name":"Privacy Violation in Error Messages","id":"Privacy Violation in Error Messages - 7311612736703362877 (sast)","description":"Method Cx58065ed3 at line 178 of /frontend/__tests__/routes/manage-organization-members.test.tsx includes PII in Error in the error message. This may result in a Privacy Violation.\n\n","tags":["security","checkmarx","sast"]}},{"id":"No Drop Capabilities for Containers - 268ca686-7fb7-4ae9-b129-955a2a89064e [Taken from query_id] (kics)","name":"No Drop Capabilities for Containers","helpUri":"https://checkmarx.com/resource/documents/en/34965-67042-checkmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"Sees if Kubernetes Drop Capabilities exists to ensure containers security context Value: metadata.name={{ubuntu-dev}}.spec.containers.name=ubuntu.securityContext is undefined Excepted value: metadata.name={{ubuntu-dev}}.spec.containers.name=ubuntu.securityContext should be set","markdown":"Sees if Kubernetes Drop Capabilities exists to ensure containers security context \u003cbr\u0